  "description": "<strong>随着移动设备的崛起，传统PC行业正在节节败退。面对这样的局面，一些传统PC厂商没有坐以待毙，而是以此为契机，大力发展自己的云计算服务。《连线》网站专栏作家MichaelV.Copeland近日发文就PC厂商面临的变革进行了解读，全文如下：</strong>据IDC数据显示，今年第一季度全球PC销量同比下滑了14%，这是该机构自1994年统计PC销量以来的最大跌幅。去年全球PC销量已经下滑了4%，该机构预测今年将继续下滑8%。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d101fb4/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240620.htm&amp;t=PC%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB+%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E2%80%9D%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240620.htm&amp;t=PC%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB+%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E2%80%9D%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240620.htm&amp;t=PC%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB+%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E2%80%9D%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240620.htm&amp;t=PC%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB+%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E2%80%9D%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240620.htm&amp;t=PC%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB+%E2%80%9C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E2%80%9D%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90\" target=\"_blank\"